About this item

Product details

Eliminate the dirt that's out of reach, but not out of sight. Extend your reach with our longest built-in crevice tool. The versatile 12V Dust buster Advanced Clean+ Cordless Hand Vacuum cleans hard-to-reach areas with less effort. 4X more powerful suction* and Power boost with the touch of a button to tackle any mess. The XL 750 mL dust bin, up to 90% more runtime*, and a battery indicator to keep you moving. Keep your hands clean with the ONE-TOUCH easy-empty dust bin. Go The Extra Length with the 12V dust buster® Advanced Clean+ Cordless Hand Vacuum.

  • Extra-long crevice tool - clean hard-to-reach areas with less effort.
  • Up to 4X More Suction Power than our leading Hand vacuum*.
  • Up to 90% More Runtime vs. Our Leading Hand Vacuum*.
  • ONE-TOUCH easy empty- Empty without touching the dirt.
  • 2 Speeds - Power boost mode for more power at the touch of a button.
  • Large Dustbin - Pick up more, empty less.
  • Battery indicator - Know how much battery is left to complete the task.
  • Washable Filter and Pre-Filter For Easy Cleaning and Maintenance.
  • Compatible with: BLACK+DECKER VF110 Dust buster Replacement Filter.
